{"tid":565320,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"喺英國鼓吹取消舞獅同粵語恭喜發財嘅女寫手-Ruan Yen-背景","createTime":"2018-02-18T23:24:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-25T22:11:09.000Z","uid":22675,"like":157,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"03c87edbcce3d68e33618785f61134cb07ecd62f","tid":565320,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T23:24:49.000Z","msg":"1. Twitter叫Yuan Ren @GirlinBeijing。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n2. 猿人報稱係WAGIC嘅寫手同主持。WAGIC係諾定咸大學嘅一個program，佢個官方Twitter叫halfthesky49，即係毛屎食嘅口號 - 女人能頂半邊天。<a href=\"https://twitter.com/halfthesky49\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhalfthesky49&d=QzOrQ7WFPs90O%2BkxkXvzim6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=e6b887a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/halfthesky49</a> <br />\r\n左膠+中國女權+新自由主義 = 最後寫出中國人消費多，所以要取代當地文化。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\r\nWAGIC重教用#metoo學普通話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\r\n<img src=\"http://elephant-room.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/IMG_1404-2-800x445.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Felephant-room.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2FIMG_1404-2-800x445.jpg&h=5726d0de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n <br />\r\n3. 喺Fodor's Travel Beijing呢本書搵倒猿人舊網站，叫mamamian。<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/gGuw3l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FgGuw3l.jpg&h=a2db466c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\r\n<br />\r\n4. 由mamamian搵倒佢以前?英國住址同埋佢其中一個ig<br />\r\n-英國前?住址:<a href=\"http://www.statsinfinity.com/domain/EEuUa9rtK5jyUBK9fXiXXA.._info.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.statsinfinity.com%2Fdomain%2FEEuUa9rtK5jyUBK9fXiXXA.._info.html&d=QzOrQ7WFPs90O%2BkxkXvzim6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=28e6a573\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.statsinfinity.com/domain/EEuUa9rtK5jyUBK9fXiXXA.._info.html</a><br />\r<a href=\"http://喺www.192.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%96%BAwww.192.com&d=QzOrQ7WFPs90O%2BkxkXvzim6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=18e485bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">喺www.192.com</a>輸入yuan ren, postcode E3 4LB，可以搵倒佢間屋重有另一個人住，由係姓任。呢個人:<a href=\"http://researchprofiles.herts.ac.uk/portal/en/persons/guogang-ren(aa9887fb-5710-4f8e-a84e-7b50f59a1094).html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fresearchprofiles.herts.ac.uk%2Fportal%2Fen%2Fpersons%2Fguogang-ren%28aa9887fb-5710-4f8e-a84e-7b50f59a1094%29.html&d=QzOrQ7WFPs90O%2BkxkXvzim6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=29f4596e\" target=\"_blank\">http://researchprofiles.herts.ac.uk/portal/en/persons/guogang-ren(aa9887fb-5710-4f8e-a84e-7b50f59a1094).html</a> <br />\r\n-佢其中一個ig叫@mamma_mian: <a href=\"https://imggra.com/user/mamma_mian/1500815913\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimggra.com%2Fuser%2Fmamma_mian%2F1500815913&d=QzOrQ7WFPs90O%2BkxkXvzim6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=5faa0000\" target=\"_blank\">https://imggra.com/user/mamma_mian/1500815913</a> <br />\r\n<br />\r\n5. 喺佢ig度搵倒一個叫Ruth Eliza Chambers嘅人，Feces Book上寫住佢係牛津出身。再Google一&amp;#21523;，發現佢做過垃圾紅網 - 今日中國(<a href=\"http://chinatoday.com.cn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchinatoday.com.cn&d=QzOrQ7WFPs90O%2BkxkXvzim6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=e1bc70c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">chinatoday.com.cn</a>)嘅寫手。<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/pM1ICD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FpM1ICD.jpg&h=4b036c5f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\r\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/Fl9b7s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FFl9b7s.jpg&h=403218e5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\r\n<br />\r\n4. 有網友喺Feces book搵倒一個曾經喺英國嘅Yuan Ren。叫我去睇睇。我覺得係佢，因為Chambers喺牛津出身，呢個猿人都係喺牛津出身，重有profile張合照，都似佢同Chambers。<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/zIswZP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FzIswZP.jpg&h=72d6e858&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\r\n左手係猿人近照，右手係Fecesbook profile張合照。<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/fwruYB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FfwruYB.jpg&h=631b170d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9dcd195d1c0993f43fcba627a9b80656527c6c63","tid":565320,"uid":22675,"like":41,"dislike":2,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T23:26:27.000Z","msg":"5. 睇吓嗰張合照有咩人like過，發現Foreign Policy Asian駐北京Editor，James Palmer like過。 咁樣，更加似係猿人嘅Fecesbook。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/g9TWwP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2Fg9TWwP.jpg&h=36f35378&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nPalmer喺Twitter個名叫Beijing Palmer。 <br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/beijingpalmer?lang=en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbeijingpalmer%3Flang%3Den&d=QzOrQ7WFPs90O%2BkxkXvzim6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=5132b225\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/beijingpalmer?lang=en</a> <br />\n<br />\n6. 猿人引用得最多嘅Twitter用戶係人民日報官方Twitter。 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.trendsmap.com/twitter/user/girlinbeijing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.trendsmap.com%2Ftwitter%2Fuser%2Fgirlinbeijing&d=QzOrQ7WFPs90O%2BkxkXvzim6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=87494558\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.trendsmap.com/twitter/user/girlinbeijing</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/mGtbAn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FmGtbAn.jpg&h=04fd5908&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢回得最多嘅用戶，第一係自己(可能因為打得多字)，第二個就有趣喇，Joanna Chiu係HKFP Tom Grundy (唔知依家重係唔係)女友。Joanna Chiu曾經喺佢自己個Blog寫過，如果中國有真正女權，佢就要失業，當時佢靠關中國女權搵食(我要搵搵佢個blog嘅cap圖)。佢見倒我貼咗佢個blog，就delete咗篇文。"},{"pid":"3ee16c28802e25bce08d594120c15b863e934221","tid":565320,"uid":22675,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T23:27:34.000Z","msg":"Joanna Chiu 事蹟，又係中國女權左膠。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=5419113&amp;page=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D5419113%26page%3D1&d=QzOrQ7WFPs90O%2BkxkXvzim6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=c6ead9fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=5419113&amp;page=1</a> <br />\n<br />\n篇文畀佢delete咗，screen cap 都冇埋 <br />\n<a href=\"https://joannachiu.com/2014/01/13/chinas-one-child-policy/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjoannachiu.com%2F2014%2F01%2F13%2Fchinas-one-child-policy%2F&d=QzOrQ7WFPs90O%2BkxkXvzim6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=f40f3631\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://joannachiu.com/2014/01/13/chinas-one-child-policy/</a> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&quot;China was relaxing its one-child policy, one of my first reactions was to worry about my job. If the government was suddenly going to become progressive on women&rsquo;s reproductive rights and other issues, what would I write about as a women&rsquo;s rights columnist based in China?&quot; <br />\n<br />\n中國正放寛一孩政策，對於此，我第一個反應是擔心我的工作。如果中國政府突然不斷改善婦女生育及其他權利，那我這個駐中國女權專欄作家，還有甚麼可以寫?"},{"pid":"532357ed99150c4565eba958ffa91ebee2b05acd","tid":565320,"uid":22675,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T23:29:44.000Z","msg":"7. Yuan Ren新Ig <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/watchmeeating/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fwatchmeeating%2F&d=QzOrQ7WFPs90O%2BkxkXvzim6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=202ab626\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/watchmeeating/</a><br />\n<br />\n8. ig入面有條link係佢portfolio。更加肯定嗰個fecesbook係佢。 <br />\n<br />\nPortfolio頭頂寫住 <br />\n「Yuan Ren, Journalist <br />\nBilingual writer and broadcaster from Beijing. Former Oxford-graduated scientist, calling London my second home.」 <br />\n<br />\n北京猿人講#metoo。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/zd0Q8l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2Fzd0Q8l.jpg&h=5956d127&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4edd0c85b57db761416c5c6030003e6b2ec1c53c","tid":565320,"uid":54344,"like":1,"dislike":44,"score":-43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T23:30:49.000Z","msg":"呢啲臭西洗唔洗咁上心啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n新年留返啖氣暖肚好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b04dd0323df79e552a3cd142539692b4f9c2480d","tid":565320,"uid":17103,"like":174,"dislike":0,"score":174,"quote":{"pid":"4edd0c85b57db761416c5c6030003e6b2ec1c53c","tid":565320,"uid":54344,"like":1,"dislike":44,"score":-43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T23:30:49.000Z","msg":"呢啲臭西洗唔洗咁上心啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n新年留返啖氣暖肚好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T23:38:20.000Z","msg":"大陸不停輸出意識型態 .. 好撚老危<br />\n到一日燒到你你就太遲"},{"pid":"6877c045aaa7776f0eb2de9a6d5162f9325bf4d5","tid":565320,"uid":132859,"like":80,"dislike":3,"score":77,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T23:46:59.000Z","msg":"成班中國帝國主義者係到用左膠語言以大欺小<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你地話南非同印度反殖建立自己國家係好事<br />\n西方同香港反中國文化殖民就係歧視？<br />\n就要自我反省同任你強姦?<br />\n屌你老母呀仆街chinese colonisers<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e359acd0941b5cb63c82c55ca523b7a70a81bf3f","tid":565320,"uid":17859,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T00:07:10.000Z","msg":"推到佢全家死絕"},{"pid":"bc6f90d9f384aa61789d0a0592f467f0935587ff","tid":565320,"uid":16004,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T00:31:47.000Z","msg":"留名關注<img sr